<p class="span2md">This was also my first time trying to integrate GLSL shaders to perform some post-processing effect. All of this was so new to me. To pull out this raindrop shader, luckily I found a piece on Shadertoy <a href="https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ltffzl">https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ltffzl</a> &ndash; Heartfelt by BigWIngs, which was beautifully done! I carefully read through the code but didn&rsquo;t fully understand it &#128549;. GLSL operates on a level that&rsquo;s still a bit beyond me. So, I ended up copying the code and tweaking some arguments to see what triggers what.</p>



